##When will the new cases in Wuhan "clear up" ? Li Lanjuan responded

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zhang Yixuan, Wang Kan, Wang Xiangyu, Qiao Wai / People's Daily client

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In Wuhan, Hubei Province, Li Lanjuan, an academician of the Chinese Academy of Engineering and a member of the high level Expert Group of the NHRC, gave an exclusive interview to the People's Daily.

When will new cases in Wuhan be cleared? How to view the current situation of fighting against "Epidemic Disease" ? Will the new crown disease break out on a larger global scale? Li Lanjuan has responded to all of these hot issues. Let's take a look:

Wuhan enters the decisive stage, must "pursue desperately the Meng Da"

Wuhan has entered a decisive phase in the prevention and control of the epidemic. We must not relax now. We must pursue all sources of infection and find out once and for all. Only (hospital) outside the infected people are "zero" , we can say that Wuhan is safe.

New Cases in Wuhan expected to be cleared by end of March

When Wuhan "clear zero" , in the final analysis to see our efforts. If we work more quickly and there are no other emergencies, such as imported cases from abroad, Wuhan may be able to "clean up" by the end of March.

We must strictly guard against imported cases

Now many areas of the country new cases "clear zero, " but must not be careless, to prevent imported cases. Test, isolate, or do it well.

If other countries do not take it seriously, the epidemic could break out on a much larger global scale

Whether the new crown disease will break out on a larger scale depends on the prevention and control efforts of other countries in the world. If they do not pay attention to epidemic prevention and control, do not pay attention to the source of infection isolation, the new crown epidemic will be more likely to break out on a global scale. Let's hope the rest of the world takes this outbreak as seriously as China does.

It is a habit to visit the ICU

As a doctor, to really understand the patient's condition, in addition to listening to the report, you must go to the ward to see. The doctor should pay attention to all the conditions of the patient. Especially in critically ill patients, many of the changes in the condition, if early detection, diagnosis, treatment, it is possible to avoid critical illness, and even avoid death.

A doctor has to be around his patients to make good decisions.

"The ideal is to be a good doctor. "

Ever since I became a Barefoot doctor in 1968, my dream has been to be a good doctor. I, too, came from a poor background. Without the Party and the People's training, I would not be where I am today. So I resolved to do something good for the people in this life. To relieve the patient's pain and save the patient's life is the biggest pursuit of my life.
